data.description: 7.37 ACRES WITH A LARGE RANCH INCLUDING A LONG DRIVEWAY SIDE ENTRY GARAGE!! ... The LEXINGTON floorplan- Must see this beautiful ranch home with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms WITH GRANITE THRU KIT(WITH ISLAND} AND ALL BATHS. Rocking chair covered front and BBQ covered back porches. This home invites you in, with the open, vaulted great room with a fireplace. Great entertaining home, is open concept, with a kitchen that offers loads of cabinets and counter space, granite, kit island, pantry, breakfast/dining room. Spacious owners suite w/trey ceilings, walk-in closet, separate tub and shower, and double vanity. Three secondary bedrooms. Rear Property line extends to Big Flat Creek. **Commission to selling broker will be reduced to 1% if not present at the first initial showing of the property.
